{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 15,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الحِجۡرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Hijr",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Rock",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 99,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 1803,
        "text": "艾列弗，俩目，拉仪。这些是天经--明白的《古兰经》的节文。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1804,
        "text": "不信道者或许要希望他们原是归顺的。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1805,
        "text": "你听任他们吃喝玩乐吧！你听任他们受希望的诱惑吧！因为他们不久就会知道的。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1806,
        "text": "我不毁灭一个城市则已，但毁灭它，就有一个可知的定期。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1807,
        "text": "任何民族都不能先其定期而灭亡，也不能后其定期而沦丧。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1808,
        "text": "他们说：受降示教诲的人啊！你确是一个疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1809,
        "text": "你怎不昭示我们一些天神呢？如果你是说实话的。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1810,
        "text": "我只凭真理而降天神，到那时，他们是不蒙缓刑的。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1811,
        "text": "我确已降示教诲，我确是教诲的保护者。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1812,
        "text": "在你之前，我确已派遣了许多使者，去教化古代的各宗派。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1813,
        "text": "没有一个使者来临他们则已，但有使者来临，他们都加以嘲笑。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1814,
        "text": "我这样使爱好嘲笑深入罪人们的心。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1815,
        "text": "他们不信我的教诲，其实，古人的常道已逝去了。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1816,
        "text": "假若我为他们开辟一道天门，而他们从那道天门继续登天，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1817,
        "text": "他们必定说：我们的眼睛受蒙蔽了，不然，我们是中了魔术的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1818,
        "text": "我确已在天上创造了（十二）宫，我为观察者而修饰天空。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1819,
        "text": "我保护著天，不许任何受诅咒的恶魔得以侵入，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1820,
        "text": "但窃听的恶魔则有明显的流星赶上它。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1821,
        "text": "我展开了大地，并把许多山岳安置在大地上，而且使各种均衡的东西生出来。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1822,
        "text": "我在大地上为你们和你们所不能供养者而创造了许多生活资料。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1823,
        "text": "每一种事物，我这里都有其仓库，我只依定数降下它。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1824,
        "text": "我派遣滋润的风，我就从云中降下雨水，以供给你们饮料，你们绝不是雨水的蓄藏者。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1825,
        "text": "我确是能使万物生，能使万物死的；我确是万物的继承者。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1826,
        "text": "我确已知道你们中先进的，我确已知道你们中后进的。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1827,
        "text": "你的主必定集合他们。他确是至睿的，确是全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1828,
        "text": "我确已用黑色的成形的黏土创造了人。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1829,
        "text": "以前，我曾用烈火创造了精灵。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1830,
        "text": "当时，你的主曾对天神们说：我必定要用黑色的黏土塑造人像而创造人。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1831,
        "text": "当我把它塑成，而且把我的精神吹入他的塑像的时候，你们应当对他俯伏叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1832,
        "text": "随后，天神们一同叩头，",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1833,
        "text": "唯独易卜劣厮不肯叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1834,
        "text": "主说：易卜劣厮啊！你怎么不叩头呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1835,
        "text": "他说：你用黑色黏土塑成人像而创造的人，我不该向他叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1836,
        "text": "主说：你从这里出去吧。因为你确是被放逐的。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1837,
        "text": "你必遭诅咒，直到报应日。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1838,
        "text": "他说：我的主啊！求你对我缓刑，直到人类复活之日。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1839,
        "text": "主说：你确是被缓刑",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1840,
        "text": "到可知的日期。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1841,
        "text": "他说：我的主啊！你已判定我是迷误的，所以我誓必在大地上以罪恶诱惑他们，我必定要使他们一同迷误。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1842,
        "text": "除非他们中你所选拔的仆人。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1843,
        "text": "主说：这是我应当维持的正路。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1844,
        "text": "我的仆人，你对他们绝无权力，除非那些顺从你的迷误者。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1845,
        "text": "火狱必定是他们全体的约定的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1846,
        "text": "火狱有7道门，每道门将收容他们中被派定的一部分人。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1847,
        "text": "敬畏者们必定在一些乐园和源泉之间，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1848,
        "text": "你们平平安安地进入乐园吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1849,
        "text": "我清除他们胸中的怨恨，他们将成为弟兄，在高榻上相对而坐。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1850,
        "text": "他们在那里不感觉疲乏，他们绝不被逐出。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1851,
        "text": "你告诉我的仆人们，我确是至赦的，至慈的；",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1852,
        "text": "我的刑罚确是痛苦的。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1853,
        "text": "你应当对他们叙述易卜拉欣的客人们的故事。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1854,
        "text": "当时，他们进去见他，说：祝你平安。他说：我们确是畏惧你们的。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1855,
        "text": "他们说：你不要畏惧，我们的确以一个聪明的男孩向你报喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1856,
        "text": "他说：我已老迈，你们还向我报喜吗？你们以什么向我报喜呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1857,
        "text": "他们说：我们凭真理而向你报喜，所以你不要绝望。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1858,
        "text": "他说：除迷误者外，谁会绝望于真主的恩惠呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1859,
        "text": "他说：使者们啊！你们有什么差事呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1860,
        "text": "他们说：我们奉派去惩治一群犯罪的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1861,
        "text": "鲁特的家族除外，我们确要把他们全都救出来；",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1862,
        "text": "但他的妻子除外，我们已预定她和其余的人同受刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1863,
        "text": "当使者们来到鲁特的家里的时候，",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1864,
        "text": "他说：你们确是一些陌生的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1865,
        "text": "他们说：不然；我们把他们一向争论的（刑罚）带来给你了。",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1866,
        "text": "我们把真理带来给你了，我们确是诚实的。",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1867,
        "text": "你应当带著你的家族在深夜出行，你要跟在他们的后面，你们中的任何人也不要回头看。你们应当往前走，一直走到你们奉命到达的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1868,
        "text": "我启示他这个判决：就是这等人，在早晨将被根除。",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1869,
        "text": "城里的居民欣然而来，",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1870,
        "text": "他说：这些是我的客人，你们不要凌辱我，",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1871,
        "text": "你们应当敬畏真主，你们不要差辱我。",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1872,
        "text": "他们说：难道我们没有禁止你与世人往来吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1873,
        "text": "他说：这些是我的女儿，如果你们要干什么。",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1874,
        "text": "指你的寿命发誓，他们必将彷徨于自己的癫狂之中。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1875,
        "text": "呐喊声在日出时袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1876,
        "text": "我使那个市镇天翻地覆，并使陶石像雨点般降落在他们身上。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1877,
        "text": "对于能考察者，此中确有许多迹象。",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1878,
        "text": "那个市镇确是在一条仍然存在的道路上的。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1879,
        "text": "对于信道者，此中确有一种迹象。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1880,
        "text": "那丛林的居民确是不义的，",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1881,
        "text": "故我惩治了他们。这两个地方都在平坦的路上。",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1882,
        "text": "石谷的居民确已否认使者们。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1883,
        "text": "我确已把我的许多迹象昭示他们，但他们背离了它。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1884,
        "text": "他们安全地凿山为屋，",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1885,
        "text": "但呐喊声在早晨袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1886,
        "text": "他们所谋求的，对于他们无济于事。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1887,
        "text": "我只凭真理创造天地万物，复活时是必定来临的。所以你应当温和地原谅众人。",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1888,
        "text": "你的主确是创造万物的主，确是全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1889,
        "text": "我确已赏赐你常常反复诵读的七节经文和伟大的《古兰经》。",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1890,
        "text": "你不要觊觎我所使他们中各等人所享受的事物，你不要为他们而悲哀。你应当温和地对待信士们。",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1891,
        "text": "你说：我确是坦率的警告者。",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1892,
        "text": "那正如我所降示分配者们的（东西）一样的，",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1893,
        "text": "他们把《古兰经》分割成若干肢体。",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1894,
        "text": "指你的主发誓，我必将他们全体加以审问--",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1895,
        "text": "审问他们生前的行为。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1896,
        "text": "你应当公开宣布你所奉的命令，而且避开以物配主者。",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1897,
        "text": "在对付嘲笑者方面，我必使你满足。",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1898,
        "text": "嘲笑者除真主外还崇拜别的神灵，不久他们就会知道了。",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1899,
        "text": "我确已知道你为他们的谰言而烦闷。",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1900,
        "text": "你应当赞颂你的主超绝万物，你应当与众人一起叩头，",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1901,
        "text": "你应当崇拜你的主，直到那无疑的消息来临。",
        "numberInSurah": 99,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      }
